dotfiles:
files to configure things like vim and zsh to my liking.

To install:

    git clone https://github.com/sierranevadan/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/_vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/_vim ~/.vim

Initialize git submodules in ~/.vim:  (there may be a better command)

    cd ~/.dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    git submodule foreach git submodule init
    git submodule foreach git submodule update
